&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience with Spark and its ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using JVM stack, build tools,&amp;nbsp; and environment (We mostly use Scala)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with public cloud environments (AWS will be a bonus), Hadoop ecosystem, SQL and NoSQL databases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High proficiency with Python and at least one JVM-based language (Scala, Java, or Kotlin)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with SQL and experience with ETL and data modeling and development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positive attitude and willingness to take ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A mindset of continuous learning and the desire to try new things&lt;/li&gt;
