&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;2chhkw&quot; data-start=&quot;2210&quot; data-end=&quot;2244&quot;&gt;Native Portuguese speaker. Must.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ksmccl&quot; data-start=&quot;2245&quot; data-end=&quot;2268&quot;&gt;Fluent English. Must.&lt;/li&gt;
