&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1790g4&quot; data-start=&quot;2349&quot; data-end=&quot;2414&quot;&gt;Strong outbound prospecting and pipeline generation experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;eyvatp&quot; data-start=&quot;2415&quot; data-end=&quot;2516&quot;&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills across email, LinkedIn, phone, and other channels.&lt;/li&gt;
